# 10 - Decision Analyzer (Multi-Agent with Profiles)
# Analyze decisions from multiple perspectives using different models

NAME decision-analyzer
INPUT decision
INPUT context DEFAULT "business"

AGENT optimist FROM agents/optimist.md REQUIRES "fast"
AGENT critic FROM agents/devils-advocate.md REQUIRES "reasoning-heavy"

GOAL frame "Frame decision: $decision. List 3-4 key factors for $context context."
GOAL evaluate "Each perspective: 3 key points max. Be concise." USING optimist, critic
GOAL synthesize "Balanced recommendation: top 3 pros, top 3 cons, 2 mitigations. Save to decision-output.md."

RUN analyze USING frame, evaluate, synthesize
